{"tid":791422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱被呀媽叫醒","createTime":"2018-08-23T18:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T00:34:16.000Z","uid":197452,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dbdbf23c10c9ee6f62f676a22e34f0a668ef801d","tid":791422,"uid":197452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:50:15.000Z","msg":"[member]原本我家姐霸撚咗我張電腦抬黎用港女最愛的MacBook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我叫佢出廳用因為我想用我部Desktop電腦 佢唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都算啦我廢撚事同個臭閪噪 咁我就過咗呀媽房睡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點知兩個鐘後被呀媽拍醒咗 佢話家姐想睡呢張床 你過翻隔離睡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係被個臭閪挽撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢都已經攞咗屋企好多錢去外國讀書架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解翻到黎仲要搞鳩我e啲未出過國嘅毒撚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去撚完讀書翻到黎唔撚識講中文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後我想講唔單止呢個社會唔公平 原來連屋企入面都可以咁唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8499c82e190d2a5828e928ee71dfa35d95f598fb","tid":791422,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:54:32.000Z","msg":"挽"},{"pid":"c446aa588bcf1b4d016f2db3a0d00a7381cfd9d1","tid":791422,"uid":136061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"加密fail"},{"pid":"9865de99d589389b17c1d165bb8a1fc49bfd8a9f","tid":791422,"uid":187227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a1c27a56d6bcdbbe9a5b4f87e6ca1c16e5df3b","tid":791422,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:18:18.000Z","msg":"出國留學vs未出過國<br />\n<br />\n樓主一係驗dna一係反思下自己點解咁唔得寵"},{"pid":"949309fe20605868fa2bf2d84a9db8eed868e928","tid":791422,"uid":32722,"l